FBIS4-14746 "drsov064_f_94032" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 National Affairs Radioactive Material Seized by Security Forces Radioactive Material Seized by Security Forces LD0104115594 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 1100 GMT 1 Apr 94 LD0104115594 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Ukrainian BFN [Text] Staff members of the organized crime-fighting department of the Zaporozhye Oblast Directorate of Ukraine's Internal Affairs and Security Service have detained a 50-year old unemployed Zaporozhye resident who was carrying in his automobile two (?flasks) each containing 55 kg of (?cesium-137). Preliminary data suggests this radioactive material was stolen from a wagon at Zaporozhye-2 railway station.
